---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section class="rounded-3xl border-[3px] border-black bg-pblue p-5 shadow-card">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
    <div class="flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full border-[3px] border-black bg-ppink font-kablamo text-4xl shadow-card1">
      S
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-pblack">Writing by</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black">seasKanon</h2>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-black">
    四季的卡农：在数学、代码、阅读与旅途中持续记录，把知识和项目做成可以长期生长的个人花园。
  </p>
  <div class="mt-5 flex items-center gap-3 text-2xl">
    <a href="/" class="rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-white p-2 shadow-card1 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-card" aria-label="Personal website">
      <Icon name="web" />
    </a>
    <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-pgreen p-2 shadow-card1 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-card" aria-label="GitHub profile">
      <Icon name="github" />
    </a>
    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-pyellow p-2 shadow-card1 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-card" aria-label="LinkedIn profile">
      <Icon name="linkedin" />
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
